      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-bold text-text-dark">Our Approach</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        We embarked on a complete creative rebrand that touched every aspect of the visual identity. From logo design and colour palette to typography and brand photography, every element was carefully crafted to capture the bold, eclectic spirit of Leopard & Roses. The new visual identity system was designed to be flexible and expressive, working seamlessly across digital and physical touchpoints.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results -->
  <section class="bg-bg-light px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-bold text-text-dark">Results</h2>
