        The creative rebrand breathed new life into Leopard & Roses. The refreshed brand presence resonated strongly with both existing customers and new audiences, driving increased customer engagement across all channels. The cohesive visual identity gave the brand a premium, distinctive look that set it apart in the lifestyle market and provided a strong foundation for future growth.
      </p>
    </div>
